PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,FKris Jepson reports on the launch of
OL,7,Fthe Cleveland hate crime strategy.
OL,9,FAuthorities on Teesside have come
OL,10,Ftogether to launch a new 10 year hate
OL,11,Fcrime strategy, following a 17% rise
OL,12,Fin hate crimes recorded in the area
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FThe launch, chaired by the Cleveland
OL,16,FPolice and Crime Commissioner, aims to
OL,17,Ffocus on education, early intervention
OL,18,Fand building resilient communities,
OL,19,Fparticularly following the riots of
OL,20,FAugust 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
