FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,FPCC, Matt Storey, told ITV News Tyne
OL,7,FTees: "We've got our hate crime
OL,8,Fcharter, which lots of organisations
OL,9,Facross Cleveland have already signed
OL,10,Fup to.
OL,12,F"We need to widen that out to the
OL,13,Fpublic now as well, and make sure that
OL,14,Feverybody knows exactly how to report
OL,15,Fit, exactly where to go, and we can
OL,16,Fbring those rates down.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,F"Also we want to make sure that people
OL,7,Fin general feel safer, that people in
OL,8,Fthis area no matter what your
OL,9,Fbackground, no matter where you've
OL,10,Fcome from, you feel safe in Cleveland
OL,11,Fand you're welcome here."
OL,13,FIn the Cleveland Police area,
OL,14,Faccording to the latest data from the
OL,15,FHome Office, there were 1,771 hate
OL,16,Fcrime offences reported in the year to
OL,17,FMarch 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
