FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,FThat was an increase of 17.4% on the
OL,7,Fprevious year. Hate incidents hit
OL,8,F1,803, a rise of nearly 14.9% and
OL,9,Fracially motivated hate crimes rose by
OL,10,F27.87%, with 1,445 recorded during the
OL,11,Fsame year.
OL,13,FShazia Noor runs the Nur Fitness gym,
OL,14,Fa local community hub that also
OL,15,Fprovides specialised support services
OL,16,Ffor women from diverse backgrounds.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News many of her clients
OL,18,Fhave suffered from hate crimes in the
OL,19,Flast few years, especially in the
OL,20,Faftermath of the riots.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,FShe said: "It's not so much if you're
OL,7,Fa Pakistani or an Indian. It's more if
OL,8,Fyou're a Muslim. That's definitely
OL,9,Fincreased, and you hear that all the
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"I've heard women say 'we walk into a
OL,13,Fshop sometimes and we feel like when
OL,14,Fwe've got our headscarf on that we are
OL,15,Ftreated differently'. When the riots
OL,16,Fhappened, they were really scared,
OL,17,Fthey just didn't know what to do, they
OL,18,Fdidn't understand who to speak to, who
OL,19,Fto call.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,F"It really scares me, as you know, I'm
OL,7,Fa Muslim myself, and sometimes I worry
OL,8,Fabout our future, about our kids in
OL,9,Fthis country."
OL,11,FThe Middlesbrough and Hartlepool riots
OL,12,Fwill have impacted on the latest data,
OL,13,Fand for those working in restorative
OL,14,Fjustice, they say it is key to educate
OL,15,Fand engage both victims of hate crime
OL,16,Fand perpetrators.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
