PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,FDave Mead is the victims services
OL,7,Fmanager in Cleveland, and also runs
OL,8,FRestorative Cleveland. He said:
OL,9,F"Bringing the offender and the victim
OL,10,Ftogether has a signifiant impact. They
OL,11,Flook at the person behind the name
OL,12,Fcalling, the abusive threats and
OL,13,Frealise, actually we're really not
OL,14,Fthat different.
OL,16,F"I've got a case about a young man who
OL,17,Fwas out in the nighttime economy, got
OL,18,Fdrunk, was thrown out of one premise,
OL,19,Fand ended up being barred by a black
OL,20,Fdoor member of staff.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773411080
OL,3,CTeesside hate crime strategy launched
OL,4,Cfollowing 17% rise in incidents
OL,6,F"He was racially abusive, racially
OL,7,Fthreatening, and then went on the
OL,8,Fdivert programme, which is intensive
OL,9,Fwork with probation, and it's made a
OL,10,Fsignificance impact.
OL,12,F"There's a wonderful letter of apology
OL,13,Fbeen written, explaining that 'I'm
OL,14,Fashamed of what I did, I didn't mean
OL,15,Fanything to hurt you, you were there
OL,16,Fto keep me safe, and I behaved
OL,17,Fappallingly', and both sides have now
OL,18,Fcome together, forgiven, shaken hands,
OL,19,Fand are moving forward."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
